## Validation Checklist

When updating any file, verify:

- [ ] Version number incremented appropriately (major/minor/patch)
- [ ] Version number follows format for file type (X.Y.Z vs X.Y)
- [ ] "Last Updated" timestamp updated with current EST time
- [ ] Version appears in all required locations (frontmatter + metadata if applicable)
- [ ] Version number is in metadata only (not in filename)
- [ ] CHANGELOG.md updated (if significant change)
- [ ] No version numbers skipped
- [ ] Version number not reused

